üåç Real-World Examples

Scenario Applied Control Type Function
Employee training on phishing Administrative Preventive
Security badge access Physical Preventive
Antivirus software Technical Preventive/Detective
Log monitoring Technical Detective
Disaster recovery plan Administrative Corrective


